#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/error_handling.rst:572
msgid "When to throw errors"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/error_handling.rst:574
msgid "The previous sections give many good reasons to avoid throwing errors, so what are some examples of cases where throwing an error is the best course of action?"
